<p><strong>Small construct, unaligned</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 15 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 17 (5d6)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 0 ft., fly 50 ft. (hover)</p>

